blood drive
even tho im not old enuf 2 donate, ive decided 2 telll as many people as possible about it. our really good friend, in sum cases brother, was severly injured in a car accident when his truck was t-boned by a STUPID drunk driver. he is in a medicated coma with no spleen, tons of broken bones, including part of his skull i believe, bruises so big and black u wouldnt imagine, a pierced bladder, and disfunctional kidneys...im not sure thats it, but thats the majority.he graduated from beyer last year. on friday the 14 beyer highschool is hosting a blood drive in his name. just 2day he used 30 units of blood, and his parents have 2 pay 4 all but 2 of them...as im sure u kno blood isnt cheap...so PLEASE cum help evan. u must be 16 with parental consent or 17 and over and parental consent is not required. u must bring ur id. its from like 5-9pm i believe, i'll fix this entry when i kno the time 4 sure. plz help me spread the word! thank u SOO much! <3 ya! sMoOcHeS!

ps: even if u cant donate, keep him and his family and friends in ur prayers and help spread the word. nething u can do is appreciated! sMoOcHeS!
